This code is from a document: https://www.ibm.com/developerworks/cn/java/j-jaas/index.html

1. How to run it?
Need to add JVM option:

-Djava.security.auth.login.config=D:\eclipse-photon-workspace\JDKAPIShadow\bin\com\fruits\jdkapi\security\jaas\login.conf

and make sure program could load the users.xml and groups.xml.


1. copy jaas.jar and jaasmod.jar to JDK jre\lib\ext(D:\JDK1.3\jre\lib\ext).
2. append "auth.policy.provider=com.ibm.resource.security.auth.XMLPolicyFile" to jre\lib\security\java.security
3. execute run.bat